rows.label: campfev11_1310_msg0001
rows.name:
So, we're taking Kei to her brother
in Lascham Cove, right?

rows.label: campfev11_1310_msg0002
rows.name:
Yes...
And we should hurry, too.

rows.label: campfev11_1310_msg0003
rows.name:
If we keep them waiting, it might
cost us their trust.

rows.label: campfev11_1310_msg0004
rows.name:
Quite.
For their sake, let's not waste any time.
